  "tosSection4Bullet3": "Upload content that is malicious, fraudulent, ou violates intellectual property rights;",
  "tosSection4Bullet4": "Interfere with the proper functioning of the Service or attempt to access data belonging to Outro users;",
  "tosSection4Bullet5": "Use the Service a send unsolicited communications ou spam.",
  "tosSection5Title": "Assinaturas e pagamentos",
  "tosSection5Para1": "Certain features of the Service require a paid subscription (\"PPro or \"EEmpresa plan). Subscription fees are billed monthly through the platform application store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) subject to their respective tTermos",
  "tosSection5Para2": "Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. You can manage or Cancelar your subscription at any Hora through your platform's account sConfigurações",
  "tosSection5Para3": "We may change assinatura fees upon reasonable notice. Fee changes will não apply a seu atual billing period.",
  "tosSection6Title": "Seus dados",
  "tosSection6Para1": "You retain ownership of the Saúde data you submit to the Service. Our use of your data is described in our Privacidade Policy, which is incorporated into these Termos by reference.",
  "tosSection6Para2": "You may Exportar your data at any Hora via the in-app Exportar feature, and you may permanently Excluir your account and Todos associated data via Configurações → Excluir Account.",
